fields.name: Stew
fields.text: A cozy, classic beef stew with tender beef, carrots, mushrooms + potatoes. Everyone will love this, especially who love traditional recipes and don't mind to eat meat

fields.name: Fruit Yogurt Salad
fields.text: Just slice some fruits, poure nice yogurt and have a nice meal. Note that you can experiment with fruits amount and fruit varieties

fields.name: Omelette with Cherry Tomatoes
fields.text: Scrumble 3 eggs, add glass of milk and fry it for a few minutes (it's just that simple). To have fancy dish slice 4 cherry romatoes and add some parsley. And don't forget about melting some butter before frying eggs

fields.name: Boiled Potato with Tuna
fields.text: Boil some potatoes and use chopped canned tuna as main dish. Also add some canned corn and list of salad to make it styilish

fields.name: Orange Fresh
fields.text: Squeeze 4 oranges with juicer. The secret of perfect fresh is bunch of mint

fields.name: Cheese and Ham Sandwich
fields.text: Perfect for people who always on the go, white bread preferable

fields.name: Simple Garlic & Parmesan Pasta
fields.text: Have pasta of any kind you like, boil it al dente, add finely chopped garlic, fresh fragrant greens and of course grated parmesan

fields.name: Salmon Grilled Steak
fields.text: Takes some time to cook, but the recipe is pretty simple: just grill fine salmons steaks on medium hot. You'll need olive oil to make it juicy, but don't overdo it if you want diet dish

fields.name: Grandma's Chocolate Cake
fields.text: Chocolate cake as your grandma would do it. So, the recipe is big well protected secret:)
